title: Very Positive News Coverage Somewhat Unlikely to Impact Inspired Entertainment (INSE) Share Price
content: News coverage about Inspired Entertainment (NASDAQ:INSE) has been trending very positive this week, Accern Sentiment reports. Accern identifies positive and negative media coverage by monitoring more than twenty million blog and news sources. Accern ranks coverage of public companies on a scale of -1 to 1, with scores closest to one being the most favorable. […]
